2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | filmmaking | magic-tricks | photography | writing | collecting | cooking |

